                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/hanxiao3580/">Hanxiety</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2010-09-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">大梦谁先觉 平生我自知</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1018320940">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1018320940" class="vote-count">1</span>
